On February 12, 2025, I served as a teaching assistant for the KAIST Industry-Academia Course titled "AI-based Design: From Analysis to Design Optimization," held in Daejeon, Republic of Korea. As part of my role, I conducted a hands-on coding session to support practical exercises for participants. I assisted [Prof. Kang](https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=tYU_Cz0AAAAJ&hl=en&oi=ao) in delivering the course effectively.
